gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Mavericks 136, Raptors 125
gameRecap.excerpt: The Mavericks defeat the Raptors, 136-125. Luka Doncic led Dallas with 30 points, 11 rebounds, and 16 assists as Kyrie Irving (29 points, three assists) and P.J. Washington (23 points, six rebounds) totaled 52 points. Immanuel Quickley (28 points, nine assists, five rebounds) and RJ Barrett (26 points, five rebounds, six assists) totaled 54 points as Scottie Barnes added 19 points, 11 rebounds, and seven assists. Dallas snaps a two-game skid to move to 34-25 as Toronto moves to 22-37.
